Package Monopoly

Class PropertySpaces

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • Monopoly.PropertySpaces
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
    public class PropertySpaces
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Class to create a property space and keep track of the space's width, height, x value, y value, property names, price, color, edge of board it is on, position on board, group it is a part of, amount of properties in its group, house count, if it has a hotel, if it is mortgaged, who it is owned by, and if it is available to be bought
    See Also:
